text: "Rumour Has It" is the fourth hit single from the Adele album 21. It was released on 5 November 2011. The song was given lots of positive reviews from music critics in. The song was written by Adele along with Ryan Tedder of OneRepublic, who also produced the song. It reached number 16 on the charts in the US and Canada. In the US, it was certified double-Platinum for shipments of over two million copies. category:2011 songs Category:Adele songs
title: Rumour Has It (Adele song)
